get a file cloud community edition or paid editions i used community edition
sign up and follow up the guide they provide or follow these steps
you should have a azure account to make a server 
creat a new viritual machine with file cloud windows in the marketplace 
select cpu version and edition
review and create server 
launch the server with RDP and your credentials
now go to c:/ and select xampp server
run the server 
go to admin portal (user= admin , password= password)
create license and path to cloud server 
create users and admins
login to the user portal
now you can seamlessly manage and share your files over the cloud and customize the server as per your wish 
